<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>HEAVENLY ABODE</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ziehin malzin mai ka hi,
 Van khu ka In ahi;
 Lei hi gamgaw mun ahi,
 Van khu ka In ahi.

[V2]
 Lauhumna leh lungkhamna haw chun,
 Nichengin ei um kim vel;
 Van khu ka Pa gam ahi,
 Van khu ka In ahi.

[V3]
 2. Thepna nasa mah lele,
 Van khu ka In ahi;
 Leiah khuolzin mai ka hi,
 Van khu ka In ahi.
 Ka phat hi a hung bei deuhdeuh a,
 Phat sawtlo kal nung leh;
 Van tung to ngei ngei ingka,
 Van khu ka In ahi.

[V4]
 3. Ka Hukdampa kawma khun,
 Van khu ka In ahi;
 Chawih-atin hungum ingka,
 Van khu ka In ahi.
 Ziechun mi phate le a um ui,
 Ka mi deih tak haw kha le;
 Kei le ziechun chawl ingka,
 Van khu ka In ahi.

[V5]
 4. Zieziekchun, ka phunchiek puoi,
 Van khu ka In ahi;
 Leiah gimthei mahleng le,
 Van khu ka In ahi.
 Thawn lohiel in va ding ing ka ting,
 Lalpa changlam pang akhun;
 Van ka Pa umna gam chuh,
 Van khu ka In ahi.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>386</hymn_number>
</song>